aps even more common than on other body parts. <br><br>&nbsp;There are other factors that can also involve dark spots on the face. They’re more likely to show up as you get older, and hormonal changes can also increase their chances. Additionally, they can show up following other kinds of damage or inflammation, including as a result of inflammatory skin conditions like eczema. 

 
